Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.24,0:00:02.97,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,To the right! To the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.97,0:00:04.71,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,To the left! To the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.71,0:00:06.24,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Now up! Now up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.24,0:00:08.37,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Bring it down! Spin around!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.37,0:00:11.20,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Wash that car like you mean it! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:30.24,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Big Mac.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.68,0:00:32.46,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.73,0:00:35.00,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,More cash to add to the stash!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.09,0:00:39.94,Rarity,,0,0,0,,How about a little break?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.94,0:00:43.72,Rarity,,0,0,0,,All of this sunshine and suds are doing a number on my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.92,0:00:45.10,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.34,0:00:50.16,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Hey, anybody seen Twilight lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.16,0:00:51.14,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.16,0:00:53.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I was just going over the numbers again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.06,0:00:55.75,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Have we raised enough to make all the repairs to Camp Everfree?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.14,0:00:57.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We've only raised half.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.73,0:01:00.32,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I counted the money four times just to be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.88,0:01:03.13,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:06.45,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We can just wash more cars. There's gotta be some we missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.66,0:01:13.02,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,I… think we're gonna have to come up with a new plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.40,0:01:15.11,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But we're running out of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.11,0:01:17.77,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,The camp fundraising deadline is next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.77,0:01:20.08,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And Pinkie Pie's already hosted a bake sale,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:22.48,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Twilight and Fluttershy had that doggy day care,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.48,0:01:25.03,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,and Sunset Shimmer and I planned this car wash.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.03,0:01:28.30,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Not to worry, darlings. It's my turn to devise a plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.34,0:01:31.35,Rarity,,0,0,0,,and I already have something amazing in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:34.94,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It will be the most profitable of all of our fundraising events!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:37.02,Rarity,,0,0,0,,The pièce de résistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.25,0:01:40.23,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Now we're talking! What's your idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.34,0:01:44.57,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Meet me in the music room later this afternoon, and I will explain everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:50.95,Spike,,0,0,0,,You got nothing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.37,0:01:52.44,Rarity,,0,0,0,,How did you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.94,0:02:20.63,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:25.18,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Three hours and still no ideas for a lucrative last-minute fundraiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.18,0:02:28.01,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Usually, window-shopping inspires me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.01,0:02:29.66,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Are you a musician?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:32.79,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Do you and your friends love to dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:33.58,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.58,0:02:35.83,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Are you unique, cool, stylish?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.83,0:02:39.05,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes, and… obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:41.42,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Do you want to win a cash prize?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.53,0:02:42.38,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.38,0:02:46.03,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Then enter the Canterlot Mall "Chance to Prance" competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:49.50,Somepony,,0,0,0,,All you need is a music video of your own original song and dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:51.77,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Then you could be prancing your way to first prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:54.31,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Sign up now at the booth near the Aunt Orange smoothie kiosk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:01.99,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, we're certain to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:09.65,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.65,0:03:12.37,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,What a nice surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:14.16,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,Not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:16.26,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Sour Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:17.26,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Sunny Flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:19.36,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Why, it's been ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:21.92,SugarCoat,,0,0,0,,It's only been a few months since the Friendship Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:22.82,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:23.50,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.11,0:03:26.38,Rarity,,0,0,0,,How is everything over at Crystal Prep Academy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.48,0:03:31.35,SunnyFlare,,0,0,0,,Oh, things at CPA have never been better since Principal Cadance took over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.49,0:03:36.52,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,Yeah. She's going to let us have the spring dance on a yacht,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:38.02,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,if we raise the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:40.13,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Sounds divine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:43.61,SomeponyLightPink,,0,0,0,,Are you signing up for the "Chance to Prance" contest, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:45.03,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:48.45,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Are you girls here to sign up for the competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:51.47,SugarCoat,,0,0,0,,We definitely aren't here because we like standing in lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.68,0:03:56.06,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,I assume you already have a video concept figured out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:59.50,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,The competition's going to be pretty fierce.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:00.59,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:05.17,Rarity,,0,0,0,,it came to me as soon as I saw that gorgeous red ruffled ensemble on the way over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:07.76,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,Tell me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:10.39,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:14.02,Rarity,,0,0,0,,each member of the Rainbooms is going to dance in a different style,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:16.38,Rarity,,0,0,0,,like flamenco, hip-hop, or street ballet
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:18.81,Rarity,,0,0,0,,and we'll wear costumes to match each genre.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:21.02,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Designed by yours truly, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:24.86,SugarCoat,,0,0,0,,That sounds like a very good concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:27.76,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:29.76,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,I guess it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:32.24,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,If you're going for way to over-the-top.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:33.55,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:35.12,Rarity,,0,0,0,,So, what's your concept?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:37.14,SugarCoat,,0,0,0,,Nothing. We don't have one yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.64,0:04:40.85,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,What she means is it's a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:42.55,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,But it's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:44.46,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,It's so original.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:47.09,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't wait to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:48.15,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.15,0:04:49.51,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,You too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:53.14,Rarity,,0,0,0,,See? It's a wonderful plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:56.79,Rarity,,0,0,0,,We'll write some lyrics for our new song, and we'll choreograph some dance moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:04:59.89,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Then our video will win a cash prize, and voilà!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.89,0:05:02.38,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You make it sound simple as pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:04.25,Rarity,,0,0,0,,That's because it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.25,0:05:06.20,Rarity,,0,0,0,,The girls at Crystal Prep even agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:07.78,Rarity,,0,0,0,,They're making a video, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:09.20,Twilight,,0,0,0,,They are?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:10.76,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Is that a problem, darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:12.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:17.04,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Just haven't heard much about my old school since I left, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:20.85,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, if you ask me, Crystal Prep has got nothing on CHS!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:22.31,Spike,,0,0,0,,I love it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:24.82,Spike,,0,0,0,,See what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:26.32,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.67,0:05:31.03,Rarity,,0,0,0,,before we get started with the choreographing of our dance moves…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.46,0:05:34.68,Rarity,,0,0,0,,there's just one tiny, teeny-weensey, little thing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:36.26,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I forgot to mention.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:37.60,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:42.74,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I would need to use our fundraiser money to buy costume materials for the video!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:46.40,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,How much is the grand prize worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:49.67,Rarity,,0,0,0,,More than double what we need to fix up Camp Everfree!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:53.99,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Then of course you can use the money for costumes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:56.49,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What the hay? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:05:57.74,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:02.51,Twilight,,0,0,0,,According to my calculations, if we lend Rarity the funds we've already raised,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:04.81,Twilight,,0,0,0,,we stand to gain four times as much money as we have now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:09.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But if we lose the video contest,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:12.22,Twilight,,0,0,0,,we'll be completely back to square one and zero dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:14.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Anyone else think this is an awfully risky endeavor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:17.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.45,0:06:18.81,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:20.66,Rarity,,0,0,0,,All right, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.66,0:06:23.96,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Who's ready to shoot our winning dance music video?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.17,0:06:30.49,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Looks like I have some fabric shopping to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:33.53,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Let's take it from the top one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:35.86,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, don't forget your cue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:38.66,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It's when Fluttershy does her triple pirouette, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.64,0:06:45.48,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And… action!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:55.99,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:58.41,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Hey! What happened to the music?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:04.52,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, it's supposed to be a triple pirouette.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:07.04,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I know. It's just that…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.03,0:07:10.61,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I… I don't think I can do one of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.87,0:07:14.04,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Darling, of course you can, darling. I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:17.30,Spike,,0,0,0,,How about you try "jazz paws" instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:18.87,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Thanks Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:21.22,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,But all these moves are pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:23.27,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:26.27,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But if we want to win, we have to bring our A-game!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:29.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Crystal Prep certainly will. They're excellent dancers,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:31.57,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and you know how they love to compete.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.23,0:07:35.84,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,How about we forget about the other teams and get back to dancing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.84,0:07:37.72,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Great idea, Applejack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:39.87,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,It's really fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:42.73,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I haven't stopped this whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.91,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Let's take it from Rainbow's entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:51.98,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And… action!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:07:59.14,Rarity,,0,0,0,,This is a disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:00.20,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:01.95,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:04.08,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Well, I can fix it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:06.23,Rarity,,0,0,0,,but I'll have to run to the fabric store before it closes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.23,0:08:08.29,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Keep practicing while I'm gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:16.22,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank goodness I budgeted for backup fabric.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.68,0:08:24.26,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Is that a disco-inspired look?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:27.69,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And a street ballet tutu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:29.44,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:32.39,Rarity,,0,0,0,,They stole my brilliant idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:42.61,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:43.90,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We got your text.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:45.51,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You said it was an emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:47.47,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Everything all right, sugarcube?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.89,0:08:48.57,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.70,0:08:50.74,Rarity,,0,0,0,,since you asked…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:55.18,Rarity,,0,0,0,,the answer is: "No!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:08:57.85,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:03.71,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Sour Sweet… and the… Crystal… Prep girls stole our video concept!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.28,0:09:06.40,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I saw them filming at the mall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:09.01,Rarity,,0,0,0,,They copied my design ideas and everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:11.28,Rarity,,0,0,0,,So of course they looked absolutely fabulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:14.78,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But the worst part is that they're all incredible dancers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.14,0:09:17.35,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Major bummer in the summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:18.94,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Tissue for your issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:20.22,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:26.59,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Everyone is counting on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:29.41,Rarity,,0,0,0,,on the video to win us the prize money for the camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:33.49,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, how could I have been such a fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:35.84,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Of course, those Crystal Preppers stole my concept!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:38.21,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I practically served it to them on a platter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:39.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Don't be too hard on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.83,0:09:45.15,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's gonna take more than one Friendship Games for those Crystal Prep girls to learn that winning isn't everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:46.65,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Maybe,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:48.47,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,this was all for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.43,0:09:50.66,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:54.79,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Your concept and costumes are really awesome, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:56.64,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,our dancing…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:58.89,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,…not so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.21,0:10:04.44,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We could barely get in a two-step without tripping over each other's boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:06.42,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Say that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:07.57,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:09.24,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You all looked great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:11.87,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Okay, maybe not great,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.91,0:10:12.97,Rarity,,0,0,0,,but, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:14.41,Rarity,,0,0,0,,but it was getting there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:17.48,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And the point is we don't have to let them win!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:19.83,Rarity,,0,0,0,,That is our video concept!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:22.84,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And I am going straight to Crystal Prep to let them know
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:25.33,Rarity,,0,0,0,,that they have messed with the wrong girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:27.13,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Who's with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.62,0:10:34.95,Rarity,,0,0,0,,No… no… no, seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.95,0:10:36.22,Rarity,,0,0,0,,who is with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:38.81,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I have no idea how to get to Crystal Prep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.89,0:10:39.82,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.94,0:10:41.94,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can try to reason with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:43.61,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We were classmates once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:45.63,Rarity,,0,0,0,,That's the spirit! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:11:00.46,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Okay, where's the dance studio?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.46,0:11:02.08,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There's a dance studio?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:03.67,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Didn't you go to this school?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.67,0:11:06.02,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, I can show you where the library is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:08.23,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Wait, shhh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:09.50,Rarity,,0,0,0,,That's their music.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.49,0:11:13.11,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.44,0:11:22.44,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,Hey, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:24.58,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,So what did you think of our routine?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:26.15,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,Scared yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.15,0:11:29.03,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Don't change the subject, Sour Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:31.05,SugarCoat,,0,0,0,,But you didn't bring up a subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.05,0:11:32.05,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.76,0:11:34.89,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,Okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.93,0:11:36.74,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You know why we're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:40.50,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You stole my… our music video idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:43.50,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Now… change your concept, or else!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.69,0:11:46.15,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but we can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.15,0:11:49.21,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:51.65,SunnyFlare,,0,0,0,,Because we care about winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:52.50,SunnyFlare,,0,0,0,,Duh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:57.22,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,And we will, because we're just about to submit our video.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.41,0:12:00.12,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You're what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:01.87,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:05.92,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Because we are still doing our video the way we planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.15,0:12:06.90,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.38,0:12:10.49,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,But there's just one flaw in your little plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:15.43,SunnyFlare,,0,0,0,,By the time you submit yours, it'll just look like you copied us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:17.70,SugarCoat,,0,0,0,,Except the worse version.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.46,0:12:26.04,Rarity,,0,0,0,,This is all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:30.40,Rarity,,0,0,0,,All the money we raised is gone, and now we have no music video!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:34.72,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I should never have convinced you all that we could pull this off in so little time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:36.16,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Are you crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:38.70,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We're great at doing stuff super-fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:40.56,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I mean, look at Pinkie Pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:44.27,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,She just built that castle made entirely out of chocolate bars while we were talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:48.62,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.86,0:12:52.07,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What I want is a new video concept!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:55.26,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So let's create one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:56.49,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:12:57.63,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:12:57.63,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:13:02.33,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,I'm sure if we all put our heads together, we'll come up with something even better than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:05.23,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Okay. I suppose it's worth a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:11.48,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I think it's working!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:13.42,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I… I got something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:16.13,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Okay, so we're in home-ec class…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.26,0:13:21.24,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,baking some apple fritters!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:26.85,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And then, a fresh batch comes outta the oven.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:31.17,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And everybody's having a great time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:33.65,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.26,0:13:38.74,Rarity,,0,0,0,,So basically, we are eating pastries at school in our music video?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:42.62,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm just kinda hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:44.74,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Anyone have another idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:46.39,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:49.02,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So… we're in the middle of the jungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:51.04,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And we're being chased by henchmen
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:52.88,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,who are shooting poison arrows at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:59.36,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,When suddenly, out of nowhere, the shadow of a giant beast appears!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:01.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:03.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Isn't this a scene from the latest Daring Do book?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:06.35,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:08.56,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That's why it seemed so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:09.54,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Nevermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:11.27,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Okay! I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:14.23,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Please, do tell…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.23,0:14:16.32,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,We'll start out on…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:17.42,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,the moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.42,0:14:20.74,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And we'll be wearing really sparkly costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.66,0:14:23.81,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,No, wait! We'll be in spacesuits!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:29.77,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,We're surrounded by gorgonzola cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:33.15,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,But then, a space doggie walks over
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:35.25,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,and start to eat the cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:39.78,Spike,,0,0,0,,Rich with buttery undertones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.83,0:14:43.53,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:45.58,Rarity,,0,0,0,,This will never work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:49.37,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:55.20,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Because the contest is for dance music videos,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:58.42,Rarity,,0,0,0,,and not one of your ideas included dancing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.61,0:15:00.20,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,But they were pretty funny, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:02.28,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I liked yours, Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:03.37,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:06.79,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:07.62,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.62,0:15:09.18,Rarity,,0,0,0,,No, I am not okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.18,0:15:10.85,Rarity,,0,0,0,,The contest deadline is tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:13.63,Rarity,,0,0,0,,and we have just been wasting time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:34.14,SugarCoat,,0,0,0,,It's no use, Sour Sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:36.30,SugarCoat,,0,0,0,,Why are we even still trying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:39.05,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,Because the deadline hasn't passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:41.47,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,We can still come up with an original song
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:45.41,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,to replace the Sapphire Shores one we've been practicing our choreography with.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.66,0:15:47.31,SugarCoat,,0,0,0,,That's highly unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:50.98,SomeponyLightPink,,0,0,0,,Why did we tell Rarity that we already submitted our video?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:53.90,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,So that we can still use her concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:56.71,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,Rarity is creative. She'll come up with something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:58.80,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,But if we don't, we have nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:01.66,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,And imagine what our classmates would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.55,0:16:11.81,SomeponyLightPink,,0,0,0,,They'll say it's our fault the spring dance had to be held in the boring old auditorium instead of on a yacht like we promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.81,0:16:13.21,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:17.09,Rarity,,0,0,0,,They just don't want to disappoint their classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.09,0:16:19.02,SugarCoat,,0,0,0,,But the Rainbooms have a band.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:22.30,SugarCoat,,0,0,0,,They'll surely have a killer original song, and we don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.30,0:16:23.26,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,Yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:26.35,SunnyFlare,,0,0,0,,Face it, Sour. We're doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:29.43,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.43,0:16:32.87,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,Rarity! How long have you been over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:36.19,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Long enough to hear that you have no original song.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:38.28,SugarCoat,,0,0,0,,Like I said. Doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.28,0:16:42.51,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Maybe you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.01,0:16:46.18,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Look, I know our teams haven't been getting along too well lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:48.62,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But I think I have a solution
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:50.60,Rarity,,0,0,0,,where everybody wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:53.94,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,We're listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.40,0:16:59.82,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,So, what's the big plan you were excited about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:10.14,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Aren't the Crystal Prep girls using this video idea now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.60,0:17:11.60,Rarity,,0,0,0,,They are, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.79,0:17:13.35,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But so are we!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:15.71,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Girls, you can come out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:21.09,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I know it's hard to believe,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:26.01,Rarity,,0,0,0,,but the Crystal Preppers here helped me to realize that competing against one another was getting us nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.01,0:17:30.22,SomeponyLightPink,,0,0,0,,And Rarity helped show us that winning was the only thing driving us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.58,0:17:34.19,SomeponyLightPink,,0,0,0,,We didn't even care if we had to steal to accomplish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:36.17,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,But that's not who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:37.56,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,Anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.86,0:17:41.89,Rarity,,0,0,0,,The Crystal Prep Academy girls have offered to help with dance moves
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:44.26,Rarity,,0,0,0,,if we'll help them with an original song.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:47.01,SugarCoat,,0,0,0,,Combining our talents is the most logical thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:50.31,SunnyFlare,,0,0,0,,We'll make one epic music video together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:52.25,Rarity,,0,0,0,,So, what do you guys think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.64,0:17:53.62,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Are you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:18:00.96,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Best! Music! Video! Idea ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:06.18,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,We can start by teaching you the words to our song.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.32,0:18:09.06,SunnyFlare,,0,0,0,,But… this is just about the Rainbooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:11.10,SunnyFlare,,0,0,0,,There's nothing about us in the lyrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:12.39,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:14.34,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Wanna help me make some changes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:16.83,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Anybody else care to work on some music?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:20.04,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,We'll get to it after I teach you some dance moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:21.32,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Music first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:22.53,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,Dance first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:23.51,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Music first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.55,0:18:24.40,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,Dance first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:25.48,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Music first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.59,0:18:26.61,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,Dance first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:28.43,SugarCoat,,0,0,0,,The order is irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:31.62,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:37.23,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:38.17,SourSweet,,0,0,0,,Camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:39.90,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Action!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:51.51,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,I feel it stirrin' deep down inside my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:53.40,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,The rhythm's takin' hold,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.43,0:18:55.28,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,And it's about to roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:58.86,Twilight,,0,0,0,,A million sparkles falling across the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:00.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,So DJ give it more,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.81,0:19:02.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's what we're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:05.44,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Dance the night away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.65,0:19:09.07,Somepony,,0,0,0,,All our friends right by our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:12.90,Somepony,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter what style you bring
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:17.12,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We're about to go on that ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:19.21,Somepony,,0,0,0,,It's dance magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.33,0:19:21.08,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Once you have it
